row.InputSentence1: Rick told his friends that he hated camping.
row.InputSentence2: They bugged him until he went camping anyway.
row.InputSentence3: One night, he awoke to a snake in his tent.
row.InputSentence4: He ran screaming from the tent.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz1: Rick refuses to even think about going camping now.
